Preconditions:
- The input array `arr` is not null.
- The length of the input array `arr` is greater than or equal to 1.
- The elements in the input array `arr` are integers.
- The elements in the input array `arr` are non-negative.

Postconditions:
- The returned value is an integer.
- The returned value represents the length of the shortest subarray to remove from the input array `arr`.
- The remaining elements in the input array `arr` after removing the shortest subarray are non-decreasing.